<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-27 17:41 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6744 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPRINT-AD-COLUMN-1000     09-27 1277
</HEADER>
