<HEADLINE>
IT'S A GREAT TIME FOR BUYING A NEW CAR 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Kansas City Star plans to move the following stories for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for AMs and PMs of Monday,
Sept. 28. If you have any questions, please call the Star's News
Desk at (816) 234-4720.
</P>
<P>
   HEASTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ Economics column by JERRY HEASTER.
Story will move in the ``f'' category.
</P>
<P>
   SENATE-DEBATE (Osage Beach, Mo.) Democrat Jay Nixon, who is
challenging Republican incumbent Kit Bond for a U.S. Senate seat,
hold the second of five scheduled campaign debates. By WILL
SENTELL. Story will move in ``w'' category.
</P>
<P>
   COMPUTER-BUG (Undated) A nervous world grapples with ways to
exterminate the year 2000 bug. By DAVID HAYES and FINN BULLERS. 2
takes. &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
