<DOCNO> NYT19980927.0195 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-27 22:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6998 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FBN-ARATON-COLUMN-NYT     09-27 0912
