<P>
   (NYT9) SANTA MONICA, Calif. -- Sept. 27, 1998 -- TV-COSTS-MEDIA,
9-27 -- Marshall Herskovitz, left, and Ed Zwick, the creators of
the 1980s ABC hit show ``Thirtysomething,'' will create four new
